    <help><![CDATA[
**What it does**
INPUT : Peptide Sequence
PARAMETERS : 
primary parameters : 
> Peptide Sequence - Input Sequence
> Sequence Start - Numerical value that represents the beginning of the sequence (default 1)
> Text Size - Size of text for helical wheel (default 32)
> Rotation - Degrees to rotate helical wheel (defaul 90)
color parameters : 
> Background Color and Text Color Selections
METHOD : Using the core features from the modlAMP python module, a helical wheel projection is constructed.
OUTPUT : _helicalWheel.png
]]></help>
